data.description: Welcome home to 110 Dogwood Drive in Williamsburg VA.  Enjoy one level living with bright and open living space and beautiful hardwood floors throughout!  Enjoy the quiet fenced back yard with new patio and lots of room to entertain friends and family!  Renovated in 2015, new washer/dryer in 2017, new hot water heater 2021. LA related to seller.
